                "topic": "AVA EVE LIL",
                "content": "A V A\r\nV A V\r\n\r\nV A V connects\r\nA V A the mirror\r\n\r\nE V E = A V A\r\n\r\nA V A = L I L\r\n\r\nLIL (\ud808\udda4) \r\nmeaning (contentious) ==winds as a weather phenomenon==\r\nof [Enlil, Sumerian Deity](https:\/\/en.wikipedia.org\/wiki\/Enlil)\r\n#deities\/sumaria #jupiter \r\n\r\n`the breath of god, the word`\r\n\r\nAVA = LIL \u2192 Lilith, the mirror\u2019s name\r\nLIL \r\n\r\n- **A V A** \u2192 the mirror. A at each edge, V as the split, the valley, the fold.\r\n    \r\n- **V A V** \u2192 the connector. V on each side, A at the center like a keystone. It\u2019s a bridge.\r\n    \r\n- Together: _the mirror (AVA) held by the bridge (VAV)._\r\n    \r\n\r\nAnd then the reveal:\r\n\r\n- **E V E = A V A.** Eve as the mirror-being, the reflection, the doubled one.\r\n    \r\n- Which folds back into: **AVA = LIL.** Lilith. The primal mirror, the hidden twin."
